 />\n郭景裕接受辯方盤問時同意，被告曾多次問警員的編號及出示委任證，希望確認其警員身分。但警員表示，他當時身穿警方提供的裝備，戰術背心及盾牌上有展示「Police」字樣，亦算是穿著警員制服，可辨別其身分，加上他評估過當時環境不出示警員委任證「比較安全」。案件押後7月27日續審。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200708/s00001/1594137094453/退休漢拒向便衣警出示身分證-警-穿警方裝備算是穿制服\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200708%2Fs00001%2F1594137094453%2F%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E6%BC%A2%E6%8B%92%E5%90%91%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%AD%89-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A9%BF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%A3%9D%E5%82%99%E7%AE%97%E6%98%AF%E7%A9%BF%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=5bd06a4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200708%2Fs00001%2F1594137094453%2F%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E6%BC%A2%E6%8B%92%E5%90%91%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6%E5%87%BA%E7%A4%BA%E8%BA%AB%E5%88%86%E8%AD%89-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%A9%BF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%A3%9D%E5%82%99%E7%AE%97%E6%98%AF%E7%A9%BF%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D&h=82ad8556\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200708/s00001/1594137094453/退休漢拒向便衣警出示身分證-警-穿警方裝備算是穿制服</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:48:44.000Z","msg":"R v Lau Yin Kum (1997) - High Court - Officer&rsquo;s number displayed on tunic was not sufficient. A citizen has the right to demand a PC on duty, whether in uniform or otherwise, to produce his warrant card for identification"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T04:30:17.000Z","msg":"算把啦仲案例？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13722e699aec2658167311b630a3306cccbd1990","tid":2099067,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"119793eeeb9b6a49cdf1140b7cf738c66e41ef20","tid":2099067,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T03:23:01.000Z","msg":"去年11月2日民主派區議員候選人在銅鑼灣維園舉行選舉集會，終遭警方中止集會；當日一名退休漢在維園閘口外吸煙，拒絕應便衣偵緝警員出示身分證，案件昨（7日）於東區裁判法院開審。警員供稱，當日他身穿警務